channel.desc: Actors Tara Lynne O'Neill and Ian McElhinney pop to the shops of Aberdeenshire in their sporty 1970s MG, impersonating cows en route. They each have a kitty of ?400 and guides in the form of Paul Laidlaw and Natasha Raskin Sharp.
